Changes in 0.7.a.3

  * Fix typo in throwing IncompatibleAPIException
  * Use remove() instead of batch_mutate() when possible 
  * Log connection errors with error_log()
  * Fix bug with remove() on Super CFs
  * Allow a microsecond timestamp to be passed in for UUID v1 creation
  * Fix CassandraUtil::uuid3() param name 

Changes in 0.7.a.2

  * Fix server revival bug 
  * Remove print statement from Connection on connection failure 
  * Add a convenience import() method to CassandraUtil 

Changes in 0.7.a1

  * Initial release
